cs.CR, cs.GT, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.CE

The paper discusses the economic incentives and decision-making of cryptocurrency exchanges regarding security investments and transaction fees. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as game theory (cs.GT) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also touches upon software engineering (cs.SE) and computer engineering (cs.CE) in terms of implementing security measures and designing secure systems.
